title: More Mormon books
description:
More books on Mormonism, including:
the journals of John D. Lee (Mormon Chronicle and journals edited by Charles Kelly)
Doing the Works of Abraham, by B. Carmon Hardy
Solemn Covenant, by B. Carmon Hardy
Early Mormonism and the Magic World View, by D. Michael Quinn
Same Sex Dynamics, by D. Michael Quinn
Mormon Hierarchy: Origins of Power, by D. Michael Quinn
Mormon Hierarchy: Extensions of Power, by D. Michael Quinn
and several other works on Mormon involvement in politics, alchemy, counterfeiting, and histories of temple worship
